description: This Chainlink VRF top 5% score Yulenka purrs with a rating of 55, and a multiplier of 5x. It has a total score of 275, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 8 for North, 1 for East, 3 for South, and 2 for West. Yulenka has the personality suit of yenta. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/80555-81324-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Yulenka [275 Votes, Top 5% Score]
